bilingual.target: 克劳迪娅和我似乎是免疫的.

bilingual.source: Black cumin is a very useful immune booster.
bilingual.target: 黑茴香是一种利于提高免疫的植物。

bilingual.source: Maybe you make plants that are immune to all bacteria.
bilingual.target: 也许你能够制造出对所有细菌免疫的植物。

bilingual.source: They are not immune, just as we are not immune to the effects of that prejudice, which can be devastating.
bilingual.target: 它们不是免疫的，正如我们无法对那些偏见的影响免疫一样，这可能是灾难性的。

bilingual.source: Phase shifted units are immune to all forms of damage, but cannot attack.
bilingual.target: 相移单位对所有形式的损失是免疫的, 但是不能够攻击.

bilingual.source: This makes humoral immune antibodies not easy to identify and attack HIV.
bilingual.target: 这使得体液免疫的抗体不容易识别并攻击HIV。

bilingual.source: Frost Nova - Will now cause damage to targets immune to immobilizing effects.
bilingual.target: 冰箭被认为有减速效果,对减速免疫的目标不会被冰箭影响,但仍然会造成伤害.

bilingual.source: Therefore, a crushing blow does not affect monsters immune to physical damage.
bilingual.target: 因此, 粉碎性打击对物理伤害免疫的怪物无效.

bilingual.source: Scientists are conducting systematic research into antigens to comBat immune disorders.
bilingual.target: 科学家正为寻找免疫的抗生原而进行有系统的研究工作.

bilingual.source: Scientists are conducting systematic research into antigens to combat immune disorders.
bilingual.target: 科学家正为寻找免疫的抗生原而进行有系统的研究工作。

yingyinNormal.en: His immune system produced antibodies that beat the viral component, but it will work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他的免疫系统对病毒产生了抗体但是它会有效的。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Rise of the Planet of the Apes》

yingyinNormal.en: Hunt is uniquely trained and highly motivated. A specialist without equal, immune to any counter measures.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亨特是经过特别训练的人，而且不达目的誓不罢休，没有人能与他抗衡，他也不露出任何破绽。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 免疫力；保护；抗扰度；免除；豁免

word_family.mean: adj. 免疫的；不受影响的；受保护的；免除的

sense_info_list.en: resistant to a particular infection or toxin owing to the presence of specific antibodies or sensitized white blood cells

examination_example.sentence: In men, the <highlight>immune</highlight> system did not appear to be involved.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在男性中，免疫系统似乎没有参与。

examination_example.sentence: It is like the <highlight>immune</highlight> system of the body, which under stress or through lack of nutrition or exercise can be weakened.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 心理健康就如人体的免疫系统，会在压力状态下或者因为缺乏营养或锻炼而被削弱。

sense_info_list.en: not affected or influenced by something

examination_example.sentence: Van Oosten believes that certain plastic objects are <highlight>immune</highlight> to decay.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Van Oosten认为某些塑料制品不会腐烂。

examination_example.sentence: Nor are highly paid managers themselves <highlight>immune</highlight> from the harm caused by the ERA's unjustified dismissal procedures.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 高薪经理自身也不能免受雇佣关系法不合理的解雇程序造成的伤害。

examination_example.sentence: Jobs that were once thought to be <highlight>immune</highlight> from automation suddenly become threatened.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 曾经被认为不受自动化影响的工作突然受到了威胁。

数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

word_family.mean: adj. 免疫的；不受影响的；受保护的；免除的

sense_info_list.en: resistant to a particular infection or toxin owing to the presence of specific antibodies or sensitized white blood cells

examination_example.sentence: For example, 10 bacteria or less of an especially deadly strain of bacteria can cause severe illness and death in people with compromised <highlight>immune</highlight> systems.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，10个或更少的特别致命的细菌菌株，就能使免疫系统受损的人得重病和死亡。

examination_example.sentence: When people are sleep deprived, there are higher levels of stress hormones in their bodies which can decrease <highlight>immune</highlight> function.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当人们被剥夺睡眠时，他们体内的压力激素水平会更高，这会降低免疫功能。

sense_info_list.en: not affected or influenced by something

examination_example.sentence: Male volunteers are more <highlight>immune</highlight> to the effects of boredom than females.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 男性志愿者比女性志愿者更容易不受无聊的影响。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
